   "file": "castle.zil",
   "line": 701,
   "endLine": 714,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-W-STARFISH ()\n\t <COND (,TIME-STOPPED\n\t\t<QUEUE I-W-STARFISH 3>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>\n\t <FSET ,STARFISH ,ANIMATEDBIT>\n\t <COND (<IN? ,STARFISH ,LAKE-BOTTOM>\n\t\t<REMOVE ,STARFISH>)\n\t       (<VISIBLE? ,STARFISH>\n\t\t<RETURN-FROM-MAP>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"   With the tiniest wiggle, the star gives evidence that it is once again\na starfish.\" CR>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
