   "source": "<ROUTINE REBUS-ANIMAL-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"The \" 'PRSO \" seems to be magically flattened upon the rebus surface.\" CR>)\n\t       (<VERB? TAKE MOVE>\n\t\t<TELL ,WONT-BUDGE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TOUCH>\n\t\t<TELL \"The \" 'PRSO \" feels cold to the touch.\" CR>)>>"
