   "source": "<ROUTINE I-UNTURN ()\n\t <RETURN-FROM-MAP>\n\t <TELL\n\"   Waves of relief. You're no longer\" AR ,TURNED-INTO>\n\t <SETG TURNED-INTO <>>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
