   "source": "<ROUTINE HEXAGONAL-BLOCK-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"It's just a small rock which has been neatly carved into the shape of an\nelongated hexagon.\" CR>)>>"
