   "source": "<ROUTINE HOTHOUSE-F (\"OPT\" (RARG <>))\n\t <COND (<AND <EQUAL? .RARG ,M-ENTER>\n\t\t     <FSET? ,FAN ,TRYTAKEBIT>>\n\t\t<QUEUE I-SN 1>)>>"
