   "endLine": 1807,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-POTION (\"AUX\" X)\n\t <SETG PLANT-TALKER <>>\n\t <RETURN-FROM-MAP>\n\t <TELL \"   Your ears tingle again\">\n\t <COND (<AND <SET X <FIND-IN ,HERE ,PLANTBIT>>\n\t\t     <NOT ,TIME-STOPPED>>\n\t\t<TELL \", and\" T .X \" no longer seems to be murmuring\">)>\n\t <TELL ,PERIOD-CR>>"
