   "source": "<ROUTINE QUEUE (RTN TICK \"AUX\" C E (INT <>)) ;\"automatically enables as well\"\n\t <SET E <REST ,C-TABLE ,C-TABLELEN>>\n\t <SET C <REST ,C-TABLE ,C-INTS>>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .C .E>\n\t\t\t<COND (.INT\n\t\t\t       <SET C .INT>)\n\t\t\t      (T\n\t\t\t       <COND (<L? ,C-INTS ,C-INTLEN>\n\t\t\t\t      <TELL \"**Too many ints!**\" CR>)>\n\t\t\t       <SETG C-INTS <- ,C-INTS ,C-INTLEN>>\n\t\t\t       <COND (<L? ,C-INTS ,C-MAXINTS>\n\t\t\t\t      <SETG C-MAXINTS ,C-INTS>)>\n\t\t\t       <SET INT <REST ,C-TABLE ,C-INTS>>)>\n\t\t\t<PUT .INT ,C-RTN .RTN>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (<EQUAL? <GET .C ,C-RTN> .RTN>\n\t\t\t<SET INT .C>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (<ZERO? <GET .C ,C-RTN>>\n\t\t\t<SET INT .C>)>\n\t\t <SET C <REST .C ,C-INTLEN>>>\n\t <COND (<AND ,CLOCK-HAND\n\t\t     %<COND (<GASSIGNED? ZILCH>\n\t\t\t'<G? .INT ,CLOCK-HAND>)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t'<L? <LENGTH .INT> <LENGTH ,CLOCK-HAND>>)>>\n\t\t<SET TICK <- <+ .TICK 3>>>)>\n\t <PUT .INT ,C-TICK .TICK>\n\t .INT>"
