   "source": "<ROUTINE CLOCKER (\"AUX\" E TICK RTN (FLG <>) (Q? <>) OWINNER)\n\t <COND (,CLOCK-WAIT\n\t\t<SETG CLOCK-WAIT <>>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (,TIME-STOPPED\n\t\t;\"don't run interrupts, but do increment moves\"\n\t\t<SETG MOVES <+ ,MOVES 1>>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>\n\t <SETG CLOCK-HAND <REST ,C-TABLE ,C-INTS>>\n\t <SET E <REST ,C-TABLE ,C-TABLELEN>>\n\t <SET OWINNER ,WINNER>\n\t <SETG WINNER ,PROTAGONIST>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,CLOCK-HAND .E>\n\t\t\t<SETG CLOCK-HAND .E>\n\t\t\t<SETG MOVES <+ ,MOVES 1>>\n\t\t\t<SETG WINNER .OWINNER>\n\t\t\t<RETURN .FLG>)\n\t\t       (<NOT <ZERO? <GET ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-RTN>>>\n\t\t\t<SET TICK <GET ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-TICK>>\n\t\t\t<COND (<L? .TICK -1>\n\t\t\t       <PUT ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-TICK <- <- .TICK> 3>>\n\t\t\t       <SET Q? ,CLOCK-HAND>)\n\t\t\t      (<NOT <ZERO? .TICK>>\n\t\t\t       <COND (<G? .TICK 0>\n\t\t\t\t      <SET TICK <- .TICK 1>>\n\t\t\t\t      <PUT ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-TICK .TICK>)>\n\t\t\t       <COND (<NOT <ZERO? .TICK>>\n\t\t\t\t      <SET Q? ,CLOCK-HAND>)>\n\t\t\t       <COND (<NOT <G? .TICK 0>>\n\t\t\t\t      <SET RTN\n\t\t\t\t\t   %<COND (<GASSIGNED? ZILCH>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   '<GET ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-RTN>)\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  (ELSE\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   '<NTH ,CLOCK-HAND\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <+ <* ,C-RTN 2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    1>>)>>\n\t\t\t\t      <COND (<ZERO? .TICK>\n\t\t\t\t\t     <PUT ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-RTN 0>)>\n\t\t\t\t      <COND (<APPLY .RTN>\n\t\t\t\t\t     <SET FLG T>)>\n\t\t\t\t      <COND (<AND <NOT .Q?>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  <NOT\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   <ZERO?\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    <GET ,CLOCK-HAND\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t ,C-RTN>>>>\n\t\t\t\t\t     <SET Q? T>)>)>)>)>\n\t\t <SETG CLOCK-HAND <REST ,CLOCK-HAND ,C-INTLEN>>\n\t\t <COND (<NOT .Q?>\n\t\t\t<SETG C-INTS <+ ,C-INTS ,C-INTLEN>>)>>>"
