   "endLine": 437,
   "source": "<ROUTINE IRON-PS ()\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,IRON-MINE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"There's no iron ore here. The vein is played out; the mine abandoned.\" CR>)>>"
