   "source": "<ROUTINE MEGABOZ-TRAP-DOOR-F ()\n\t <COND (<AND <EQUAL? ,HERE ,MEGABOZ-HUT>\n\t\t     <TOUCHING? ,MEGABOZ-TRAP-DOOR>\n\t\t     <NOT <IN? ,PROTAGONIST ,LADDER>>>\n\t\t<CANT-REACH ,MEGABOZ-TRAP-DOOR>)\n\t       (<AND <VERB? ENTER>\n\t\t     <EQUAL? ,HERE ,MEGABOZ-HUT>>\n\t\t<DO-WALK ,P?UP>)>>"
