   "line": 2227,
   "endLine": 2233,
   "source": "<ROUTINE QUARRY-SHADOW-PS ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? ENTER>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,QUARRY>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"You are; the tree's shadow covers the entire floor of the quarry.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <DO-WALK ,P?DOWN>)>)>>"
