   "endLine": 765,
   "source": "<ROUTINE V-BEHEAD (\"OPTIONAL\" (CALLED-BY-V-HANG <>))\n\t <TELL \"You usually need a \">\n\t <COND (.CALLED-BY-V-HANG\n\t\t<TELL \"noose\">)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"axe\">)>\n\t <TELL \" to do this\">\n\t <COND (<AND <NOT <FSET? ,PRSO ,ACTORBIT>>\n\t\t     <NOT <EQUAL? ,PRSO ,ME>>>\n\t\t<TELL\n\", and besides, it doesn't look like\" T ,PRSO \" even has a \">\n\t\t<COND (.CALLED-BY-V-HANG\n\t\t       <TELL \"neck\">)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <TELL \"head\">)>)>\n\t <TELL ,PERIOD-CR>>"
